document_data.name: ''Timestave''
document_data.creator: [[Labelas Enoreth]]
document_data.mainbody: The '''''Timestave''''' was an [[enchanted]] [[quarterstaff]] wielded by [[Labelas Enoreth]].
document_data.Powers: This unique powerfully enchanted quarterstaff could cast a variety of [[spell]]s when striking a target including ''[[age plant]], [[age object]], [[age creature]], [[age dragon]]'' and the reverse of those spells.
